textBeforeTable: Music Read the full recap Recap Stan is flying his girlfriend Penny Dessertine in his two-seater plane and a storm comes up. She panics and begs him to land, and Stan says that they’re close. As Penny looks out the window, she sees something huge fly by. Stan dismisses it as a bird and tells her to close her eyes as relax She does so, but there’s a crash as something rips through the windshield and pulls Stan out. Penny screams in horror as the plane plummets toward the ground...
